{"tid":139334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新手求救 領養左隻唐唐","createTime":"2017-03-01T10:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T01:54:52.000Z","uid":88349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f7dcc5b480086f78343a1f888abaeb7548d9ba8","tid":139334,"uid":88349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n最近接左隻唐唐<br />\n黎左屋企個零星期都仲係好怕咁<br />\n目前仲係困係籠入面，出黎個陣就會周圍大小便。佢本身係山上流浪既，要盡快去檢查同沖個涼，但係一直都好抗拒戴狗帶同入袋，根本帶唔到佢出去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於本身無經驗<br />\n好想請教巴絲要點訓練佢"},{"pid":"a8dae62a22ff22b89a2ce6c1d3bea2e028de893f","tid":139334,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:41:58.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"8323dd45c32433a4313d1b5941f4bd3812ab4564","tid":139334,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:44:01.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"f35e365a18955e8f87460d96ebf27ae02a98eddd","tid":139334,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"玩波波<br />\n有噹噹果種<br />\n掉出去等佢執返嚟<br />\n唔好困入籠啦<br />\n<br />\n教佢去一個地方大小便<br />\n佢想去果陣會轉幾圈一路聞地下<br />\n見到就帶佢去<br />\n<br />\n陌生地方未慣姐我諗<br />\n俾d時間<br />\n多d同佢玩"},{"pid":"d8f120b4e06db1fd3a1fb333b2ab9c7659e7fbe9","tid":139334,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"Hello 無圖？"},{"pid":"3b46a5dae9d848e671a84fe5dcad8b0f1264f25e","tid":139334,"uid":88349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1d8um4n7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1d8um4n7&h=8a23aeb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cba906ef6ba71764ef760cc9662807f9f713a5a","tid":139334,"uid":13307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e16692a26d87e11b98b095d70c77ad873a7223c","tid":139334,"uid":88349,"like":0,"disl